WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:04.566
My best tips for getting through immigration controls in the United States. 

00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:05.097
1st tip, 

00:00:05.097 --> 00:00:06.691
know 1 minimum of English, 

00:00:06.691 --> 00:00:08.875
The test will not be done in French. 

00:00:08.881 --> 00:00:11.698
You have to speak 1 minimum in English and today it is clearly 

00:00:11.698 --> 00:00:14.560
possible with the applications et cetera So there is no excuse. 

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:18.115
Don't panic and be as natural as possible. 

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:21.909
If the immigration officer sees that you are not comfortable with your answers, 

00:00:21.909 --> 00:00:23.094
that you start to stutter, 

00:00:23.094 --> 00:00:26.472
that you are not sure about your plan and why you come to the United States, 

00:00:26.472 --> 00:00:29.675
you will pass 1 second check and you will pass 1 bad quarter of an hour. 

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:32.760
Answer the questions clearly and simply. 

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:34.875
If asked why you are in the United States, 

00:00:34.875 --> 00:00:35.632
he simply said, 

00:00:35.632 --> 00:00:38.141
if asked if you have ever visited the United States, 

00:00:38.141 --> 00:00:39.041
he said yes or no. 

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:40.209
