00:00:40.209 --> 00:00:44.924
If you are going on Insta and planning to go to the U.S. for 3 months, 

00:00:44.924 --> 00:00:47.514
I advise you to go simply for 85 days, 

00:00:47.514 --> 00:00:48.377
eighty days, 

00:00:48.377 --> 00:00:50.237
but not 90 days completely. 

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:50.884
The thing is, 

00:00:50.884 --> 00:00:52.569
if you go away for 90 days completely, 

00:00:52.569 --> 00:00:54.513
the question may arise as to whether you are 

00:00:54.513 --> 00:00:56.717
going to immigrate to the United States illegally. 

00:00:56.840 --> 00:00:57.517
And finally, 

00:00:57.517 --> 00:00:58.194
last advice, 

00:00:58.194 --> 00:01:00.747
leave with a minimum of 1 money on your account. 

00:01:00.747 --> 00:01:01.997
Depending on the state, 

00:01:01.997 --> 00:01:03.404
this can change of course, 

00:01:03.404 --> 00:01:06.581
but for example if you go to California for a full 3 months, 

00:01:06.581 --> 00:01:08.874
